%% Export: docs/diagrams/architecture-cicd-sequence.png
%% CI/CD sequence — build once, promote by digest, GitOps deploy
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Dev as Developer
  participant GH as GitHub
  participant ADO as Azure DevOps
  participant ACRd as ACR dev
  participant ACRs as ACR stage
  participant ACRp as ACR prod
  participant Argo as Argo CD
  participant AKS as AKS cluster

  rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    Note over Dev,AKS: CI — build, scan, push to dev ACR
    Dev->>GH: Push code to main (or feature branch)
    Dev->>ADO: Trigger CI pipeline (manual by default)
    ADO->>GH: Checkout mono-repo
    ADO->>ADO: Lint / test (placeholder)
    ADO->>ADO: docker build apps/service/Dockerfile
    ADO->>ACRd: docker push (tag = commit SHA)
    ADO->>ACRd: Resolve image digest
    ADO->>ADO: Trivy scan (HIGH/CRITICAL fail build)
    ADO->>GH: Update gitops/envs/dev/values-*.yaml
    ADO->>GH: Open GitOps PR (digest bump)
    Dev->>GH: Review and merge PR
  end

  rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over GH,AKS: GitOps deploy — dev (auto-sync)
    Note over Argo: root app-of-apps syncs apps-dev + platform-dev
    Argo->>GH: Watch gitops/ + charts/
    Argo->>AKS: Helm sync workloads → dev namespace
    Argo->>AKS: Sync policies (Quota, NP, LimitRange)
    AKS->>ACRd: Pull image by digest
  end

  rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
    Note over Dev,AKS: Promote to stage — no rebuild
    Dev->>ADO: Trigger promote-to-stage pipeline
    ADO->>GH: Read digest from dev values file
    ADO->>ACRd: Validate source image exists
    ADO->>ACRs: az acr import (same digest)
    ADO->>GH: Update gitops/envs/stage/values-*.yaml
    ADO->>GH: Open promotion PR
    Dev->>GH: Merge PR
    Argo->>AKS: Auto-sync apps-stage + platform-stage
    AKS->>ACRs: Pull image by digest
    ADO->>AKS: Smoke test stage.boutique.example.com
  end

  rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
    Note over Dev,AKS: Promote to prod — approval + manual sync
    Dev->>ADO: Trigger promote-to-prod pipeline
    Note over ADO: Azure DevOps environment approval (promote-prod)
    ADO->>GH: Read digest from stage values file
    ADO->>ACRs: Validate source image exists
    ADO->>ACRp: az acr import (same digest)
    ADO->>GH: Update gitops/envs/prod/values-*.yaml
    ADO->>GH: Open promotion PR (CODEOWNERS review)
    Dev->>GH: Merge PR
    Dev->>Argo: Manual Sync apps-prod + platform-prod
    Argo->>AKS: Helm sync → prod namespace
    AKS->>ACRp: Pull image by digest
    ADO->>AKS: Smoke test boutique.example.com
  end
